hadiths[61]{hadithnumber,text}:
3641,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sey sadqey ka sawab ziyada hai? aap ney farmaya : to us waqt sadqa karey jab to tandurust ho, tujhey maal ki zarurat ho, faqr (gharibi) ka dar ho aur zindagi ki ummid ho. aur sadqa karney mein takheer na kar yahan tak ke jab rooh halaq tak aa jaey to phir to kahe : falan ko itna dey do. ab to tera maal dusron ka ho chuka."
3642,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik dafa) farmaya : tum mein sey kis shakhs ko apney waris ka maal apney maal sey badh kar piyaaraa hai? sahaba ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum mein sey har shakhs ko apna maal hi waris key maal sey ziyada piyaaraa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs bhi aisa nahin jisey apney waris ka maal apney maal sey ziyada piyaaraa na ho kyonkey tera maal to wo hai jo tu ney kharch kar liya aur jo to chhod gaya, wo terey waris ka maal hai."
3643,"Hazrat Mutrif apney walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu)) sey bayan farmatey hain ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (اَلْھٰکُمْ التَّکَاثُرُ حَتّٰی زُرْتُمُ الْمَقَابِرِ),""tum ko kasrat ki khahish aur talab ney (Allah taala aur aakhirat sey) ghafil rakha yahan tak ke tum ney qabren dekh lein.'' ki tafseer mein farmaya : insan kehta hai : mera maal , mera maal , halanke tera maal to wo hai jo tuney kha kar khatam kar diya ya pehan kar boseedah kar diya ya sadqa khairat kar key us ka sawab jari kar liya."
3644,"Hazrat Abu Habeeb Taai bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs ney martey waqt chand deenar Allah Taala key raastey mein kharch karney ki wasiyat ki to Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey is barey mein puchha gaya. unhoney kaha ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hai : jo shakhs martey waqt ghulam azad karta hai ya sadqa karta hai, wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo khud sair honey key baad tohfa bhejta hai."
3645,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman apni kisi chiz key barey mein wasiyat karna chahta hai, uskey liye do raaten bhi baghair wasiyat key guzaarnaa jayez nahin balke wasiyat uskey paas likhi hui mojud honi chahiye."
3646,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman shakhs key liye, jis key paas koi chiz hai jis mein wo wasiyat karna chahta hai, ye munasib nahin ke wo do raaten bhi guzaarey magar is haal mein ke uskey paas uski wasiyat tahreeri surat mein mojud honi chahiye."
3647,Hazrat Naafey ney isey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol batlaya hai.
3648,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman aadmi key liye jayez nahin ke is par teen raaten guzren magar is haal mein ke uski wasiyat uskey paas likhi honi chahiye. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya jab sey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman suna hai, us waqt sey meri wasiyat (har waqt) merey paas mojud rehti hai."
3649,"Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis musalman shakhs key paas koi chiz ho jis mein wo wasiyat karna chahta hai, uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo teen raaten bhi guzaarey magar is haal mein ke uski wasiyat uskey paas likhi honi chahiye."
3650,Hazrat Talha bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi oofaa sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney koi wasiyat farmaee thi? unhoney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : phir musalmanon par wasiyat karna kyon zaroori qarar diya gaya hai? unhoney farmaya ke aap ney Kitabu-llah par amal karney ki wasiyat farmaee.
3651,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (wafat key waqt) koi deenar, dirham, bakri, oont nahin chhodey aur na aap ney (maal ya khilaafat sey mutalliq) koi wasiyat farmaee."
3652,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (apni wafat key waqt) koi dirham, deenar, bakri aur oont waghera nahin chhod kar gaey. aur na aap ney koi wasiyat ki."
3653,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney koi dirham , koi deenar , koi bakri ya koi oont nahin chhoda , aur na aap ney koi wasiyat hi farmaee. (hadees ke raawi) Jafar bin Muhammad ney (riwayat bayan kartey huye) deenar aur dirham ka zikr nahin kiya."
3654,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : log kehtey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasiyat farmaee hai (jabkey haqiqat ye hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney peshab karney key liye thal mangwaya. itney mein aap key aa'zaa dheley pad gaey (aur aap Allah ko piyarey ho gaey). mujhey (aap ki wafat ka) pata bhi nahin chala to aap ney kis ko wasiyat farma di?"
3655,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to aap key paas merey siwa koi aur na tha. aap ney thaal mangwaya.
3656,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main is qadr bimar ho gaya ke maut ko jhankney laga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri bimar pursi key liye tashrif laye. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas bahut ziyada maal hai aur meri beti key siwa mera koi waris nahin. to kya main apna do tihai maal sadqa kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : nisf (aadha)? farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : eik tihai? farmaya : eik tihai, eik tihai bhi ziyada hi hai. to apney waarison ko maal-daar chhod kar jaey to wo behtar hai bajaey iskey ke to unhen faqir bana kar chhod jaey. wo logon sey (bheek) maangtey phiren."
3657,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri bimar pursi ko tashrif laye. main un dino Makka mein tha. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney sarey maal ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : nisf (aadha)? farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : to phir tihaai? aap ney farmaya : haan tihai. tihai bhi ziyada hi hai. to apney waarison ko maal-daar chhod kar marey to behtar hai bajaey iskey ke to unhen faqir chhod kar marey ke wo logon key samney haath phelatey rahen."
3658,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Makka Mukarrama mein Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us (Saad) ki bimar pursi ko aaya kartey they kyonkey aap is baat ko napasand farmatey they ke koi shakhs us jagah faut ho jahan sey wo hijrat kar chuka hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Saad bin Ifraa par reham farmaey. (kyonkey wo Makka mein faut ho gaey they) us waqt meri eik beti hi thi. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main apney sarey maal ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : ji ! nisf (aadha)? farmaya, nahin. mainey kaha : tihai? farmaya : haan tihai balke tihai bhi ziyada hi hai. to apney waarison ko maaldaar chhod kar jaey to behtar hai us baat sey ke unhen faqir chhod jaey. wo logon key haath takte rahen."
3659,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki aal mein sey kisi ney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Saad bimar ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to Hazrat Saad ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney sarey maal (ko sadqa kerney) ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. phir (raawi ney sabiqa) hadees bayan ki.
3660,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kartey hain ke wo Makka mein bimar ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye. jab Saad ney aap ko dekha to roney lagey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main is jagah faut ho jaaunga jahan sey mainey hijrat ki thi? farmaya : Inshallah nahin. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main apney sarey maal ki Fisabililah sadqa karney ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. us ney kaha : do tihaai wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. us ney kaha : nisf (aadhe) ki wasiyat kar dun? farmaya : nahin. us ney kaha : phir tihaai ki wasiyat kar dun? farmaya, tihaai. tihaai  bhi ziyada hi hai. to apney beton ko maaldaar chhod jaey to ye us sey behtar hai ke to in ko faqir chhod jaey. wo logon key samney haath phelatey phiren."
3661,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri bimari key doran mein meri bimar pursi ko tashrif laye aur farmaya : tum ney koi wasiyat ki hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : kitney maal ki? mainey kaha : apna tamam maal fisabililah sadqa karney ki. aap ney farmaya : apney bachchon key liye kya chhoda hai? mainey kaha : wo maal-daar hain. farmaya : sirf daswen hissey ki wasiyat karo. aap ki aur meri takraar jari rahi yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : chalo teesrey hissey ki wasiyat kar lo. wesay teesra hissa bhi ziyada hi hai."
3662,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri bimari key doran mein bimar pursi key liye tashrif laye. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney sarey maal ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : nisf (aadhey)? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : tihai? aap ney farmaya : tihai ! tihai bhi bahut hai.
3663,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimar pursi key liye tashrif ley gaey. Saad (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney do tihai maal ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. unhoney kaha : nisf (aadhey) ki wasiyat kar dun? farmaya : nahin. unhoney kaha : to phir tihai ki wasiyat kar dun? farmaya : (tihai ki wasiyat kar do.) wesay tihai bhi ziyada hi hai. to apney waarison ko maaldaar chhod kar jaey to ye behtar hai us sey ke to unhen faqir aur nadaar chhod kar jaey ke wo logon sey maangtey phiren.
3664,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke agar log tihai sey kam kar key chothai tak wasiyat karen to behtar hai kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : tihai bhi ziyada hi hai.
3665,Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye. main bimar tha. mainey kaha : meri aulad sirf eik beti hai to kya main apna sab maal fisabililah kharch karney ki wasiyat kar dun? Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : nisf (aadhey) maal ki wasiyat kar dun? Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : to tihai ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : tihai ki kar do. wesay tihai bhi ziyada hi hai.
3666,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid mohtaram jange-uhad key din shaheed ho gaey. chhe betiyan aur apney zimmey bahut qarz chhod gaey. jab khajuron ki katai ka waqt aaya to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aap jantey hain ke merey walid uhad ki jang key din shaheed ho gaey they. wo apney zimmey kafi qarz chhod gaey hain. main chahta hun (aap tashrif laeyn taake shayad) qarz chahey (qarz chahney wale) hazraat aap ka lihaz rakhen (aur riayat kar den). aap ney farmaya : tum jaao aur har qism ki khajuron key alag alag dher laga do. main aisa karney key baad phir aap ko bula laya, jab qarz khuwahon (qarz chahney walo) ney aap ko dekha to wo mujh par bahut bhadke. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey tarze-amal ko dekha to aap (uthey aur) sab sey badey dher key ird-gird chakkar laganey lagey. teen chakkar laganey key baad aap is par beth gaey, phir farmaya : apney qarz khuwahon (qarz chahney walon) ko bulaao. aap un sab ko maap maap kar detey rahey yahan tak ke Allah Taala ney merey walid ka sab qarz utaar diya. main to is baat par bhi razi tha ke merey walid mohtaram ka qarz ada ho jaey, chahey (chaahey) kuchh bhi baqi na rahey. (magar qarz ki adaegi key bawajood) eik khajoor bhi kam nahin hui."
3667,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke merey walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Haram (Raziallahu anhu) ) faut ho gaey. unkey zimmey ka kafi qarz tha. main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur guzarish ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid mohtaram shaheed ho gaey hain. un par kafi qarz hai. unhoney (adaegi key liye) koi chiz nahin chhodi siwaye iskey jo khajuren phal dengi, jabkey khajuron ki puri fasal bhi unka qarz na chuka sakeygi balke kaee saal lagengey, lihaza aey Allah key Rasool ! merey sath tashrif ley chalen taake qarz khuwah (qarz chahney wale) mujh sey bad-suluki na keren, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif la kar har dher key gird ghoomtey rahey aur barkat aur salamti ki dua farmatey rahey, phir ooper beth gaey aur qarz khuwahon (qarz chahney walon) ko bulaya. phir unhen pura pura qarz ada kiya. phir bhi itni khajuren bachi rahin jitni un logon (qarz khuwahon) ney lein."
3668,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (merey walid mohtaram) Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Haram (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey aur bahut sa qarz apney zimmey chhod gaey. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey darkhaast ki ke aap unkey qarz khuwahon (qarz chahney walon) sey sifarish farmaain ke wo unkey zimmey kuchh qarz maaf kar den. aap ney un sey kaha magar un logon ney baat na maani. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jaao ! har qism ki khajuren alag alag rakho. ajwa alag, azaq ibne Zaid alag, isi tarah dusri. phir mujhey pegham bhejna. mainey isi tarah kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye. aur unkey ooper ya darmiyan mein beth gaey aur farmaya : inhen maap kar do. mainey unhen maap-maap kar deni shuru kar din yahan tak ke sab ko unka qarz pura pura ada kar diya, phir bhi meri khajuren bach gaeen goya ke un mein kuchh bhi kami na aai."
3669,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Yahudi ney merey walid mohtaram sey kuchh khajuren leni thin. wo jange-uhad key din shaheed ho gaey aur do baagh chhod gaey. lekin (merey andazey key mutabiq) us Yahudi ka qarz dono baaghon key phal key barabar tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Yahudi sey kaha : kya to itni riayat kerega ke nisf (aadha) qarz is saal ley ley aur nisf (aadha) baad mein ley lena. Yahudi ney inkar kar diya. to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jab khajuron ki katai puri ho jaey to mujhey batana. chunanche mainey waqt par bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye. nichey sey khajuren maap-maap kar di jati rahin aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) barkat ki dua farmatey rahey. yahan tak ke chhotey baagh hi sey hamney usey us ka qarz pura kar diya, phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sathiyon key paas taza khajuren aur pani laya, sab ney khaya aur piya. phir aap ney farmaya : ye wo nematen hain jinkey barey main tum sey sawal kiya jaeyga."
3670,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey walid mohtaram faut huye to unkey zimmey bahut sa qarz tha. mainey unkey qarz khuwahon (qarz chahney walon) ko pesh kaash! ki ke wo apney qarz key iwaz is saal ka sara phal ley lein. wo na maaney. unka khayal tha ke is phal sey qarz pura nahin hoga, chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur puri baat keh sunai. aap ney farmaya : jab to khajuren kaat kar khaliyiaan mein rakh ley to mujhey ittilaa karna. jab mainey khajuren kaat kar khaliyiaan mein rakh lein to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, chunanche aap, Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma key sath tashrif laye aur khaliyiaan par beth kar barkat ki dua ki. phir farmaya : apney qarz khuwahon (qarz chahney walon) ko bulaao aur unhen unka qarz pura pura detey jaao. jis kisi ka bhi merey walid marhum key zimmey qarz tha, mainey un sab ko ada kar diya, phir bhi tehra wasq bach gaey. mainey aap sey tazkira kiya to aap muskuraaey aur farmaya : ja kar Abu-Bakar aur umr ko bhi bataoo. mainey unhen bataya to wo kehney lagey : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wahan dua ki thi to hamein usi waqt yaqin ho gaya tha ke aisey hi hoga."
3671,"Hazrat Amr bin Khaarija (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya aur kaha : Allah Taala ney har haq waley ko us ka haq dey diya hai, lihaza ab waris key liye wasiyat nahin ki ja sakti."
3672,"Hazrat ibne Khaarija (Raziallahu anhu) ney zikr farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko apni sawari par khutba irshad farmatey dekha aur suna hai, jabkey sawari jugaali kar rahi thi aur us ka lu'aab (merey kandhon key darmiyan) gir raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya : Allah Taala ney har shakhs ko virasat mein sey hissa dey diya hai, lihaza waris key liye wasiyat jayez nahin."
3673,"Hazrat Amr bin Khaarija (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney har haq waley ko us ka haq dey diya hai, lihaza kisi waris key barey mein (kami ya beshi ki) wasiyat nahin ki ja sakti."
3674,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ye aayat utri : (وَاَنْذِرْ عَشِیْرَتَکَ الْاَقْرَبِیْنَ), ""apney qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaiye.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Quraish ko dawat di. aap ney umoomi taur par bhi sab ko daraya aur khas khaas naam ley kar bhi. aap ney farmaya : aey Kaab bin Luaee ki aulad ! aey Murra bin Kaab ki aulad ! aey Abd Shams ki aulad aey Abd Munaaf ki aulad ! aey Haashim ki aulad ! aey Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! apney aap ko aag sey bacha lo. aey Fatima ! to bhi apney aap ko aag sey bacha ley. main tumharey liye Allah Taala ki taraf sey kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. albatta meri tum sey rishte-daari hai. main iskey taqaazey purey karta rahunga."
3675,Hazrat Musa bin Talha sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abd munaaf ki aulad ! apney aap ko Rab taala (key azab) sey bacha lo. main tumharey liye Allah Taala ki taraf sey kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. aey Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! apney aap ko apney Rab karim (key azab) sey chhuda lo. main tumharey liye Allah Taala ki taraf sey kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. lekin mera tum sey rishta hai jis ka haq main ada karta rahunga.
3676,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par ye aayat nazil hui : (وَاَنْذِرْ عَشِیْرَتَکَ الْاَقْرَبِیْنَ),  ""aur (aey peghambar ! ) apney qaribi rishtey-daaron ko (azabe-Ilaahi sey) daraaiye.'' to aap ney farmaya : aey jamaat Quraish ! apney aap ko (toheed key zariey sey) Allah Taala (key azab) sey chhuda lo. main tumharey liye Allah Taala ki taraf sey kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. aey Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! main tumharey liye bhi Allah Taala ki taraf sey kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. aey Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ! main terey liye bhi Allah Taala ki taraf sey kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. aey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki phuphi Safiya ! main tujhey bhi Allah Taala (key azab) sey koi faeyda nahin dey sakunga. aey Muhammad ki beti Fatima ! (duniya mein) mujh sey jo chahey mang ley magar Allah Taala (key azab) sey main tujhey koi faeyda nahin pahuncha sakunga."
3677,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par ye aayat nazil hui : (وَاَنْذِرْ عَشِیْرَتَکَ الْاَقْرَبِیْنَ),  ''apney qaribi rishtey-daaron ko daraaiye.'' to Rasulullah khadey huye aur farmaya : aey jamaat Quraish ! apney aap ko Allah Taala (key azab) sey chhuda lo. main Allah Taala (key azab) sey tumhen koi faeyda nahin pahuncha sakunga. aey Abd Munaaf ki aulad ! main tumhen Allah Taala (ki pakad) sey koi kifaayat nahin kar sakunga. aey Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ! main tujhey Allah Taala ki taraf sey koi faeyda nahin pahuncha sakunga. aey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki phuphi Safiya ! main tujhey Allah Taala ki taraf sey kuchh faeyda nahin pahuncha sakunga. aey Fatima ! to (duniya mein) mujh sey jo chahey mang ley, main tujhey Allah Taala ki taraf sey koi faeyda nahin pahuncha sakunga."
3678,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab ye aayat utri : (وَاَنْذِرْ عَشِیْرَتَکَ الْاَقْرَبِیْنَ),  ''apney qaribi rishtey-daaron ko (Allah taala key azab sey) daraaiye.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Fatima binte Muhammad ! aey Safiya binte Abdul-Muttalib ! aey Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! main tumhen Allah Taala (ki pakad) sey koi faeyda nahin pahuncha sakunga. duniyaawi maal mein sey mujh sey jo chaho mang lo."
3679,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : meri walida ki jaan achcha nikal gaee. agar usey baat cheet ka moqey milta to wo zarur sadqa karti. kya main ab uski taraf sey sadqa kar sakta hun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. chunanche us shakhs ney apni walida ki taraf sey sadqa kiya.
3680,"Hazrat Saeed bin Amr bin Sharjeel bin Saeed bin Saad bin Ubada apney walid sey aur wo apney dada Hazrat Saeed bin Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke (merey walid mohtaram) Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath kisi jang mein gaey huye they ke Madina Munawra mein un ki walida mohtarma ki wafat ka waqt aa gaya. un sey kaha gaya : koi wasiyat farmaiye. wo kehney lagin : main kya wasiyat karun? maal to Saad ka hai. wo Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) key wapis aaney sey pehley hi faut ho gaeen. phir jab Saad aaye to un sey is baat ka tazkira kiya gaya, chunanche wo (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir ho kar) kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar main un ki taraf sey sadqa karun to kya unhen faeyda hoga? Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. Saad kehney lagey : mera falan falan baagh un ki taraf sey sadqa (jaariya) hai."
3681,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab insan mar jata hai to teen Suraton key ilawa, uskey sab amal munqata' ho (ruk) jatey hain. (aur wo ye hain : ) sadqa jaariya, wo ilm jis sey (baad mein bhi) faeyda uthaya jata rahey aur nek aulad jo uskey liye dua karti rahey."
3682,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : merey walid mohtaram faut ho gaey hain. wo kafi maal chhod gaey hain lekin unhoney koi wasiyat waghera nahin ki. agar main un ki taraf sey (apney taur par) sadqa kar dun to kya un ki ye ghalati maaf ho jaeygi? aap ney farmaya : haan.
3683,"Hazrat Sareed bin Suwed Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat aqdas mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya ke meri walida ney (wafat key waqt) wasiyat ki thi ke meri taraf sey eik ghulam azad kiya jaey. merey paas eik habshi londi hai. agar main usey azad kar dun to kya meri zimmey-daari ada ho jaeygi? aap ney farmaya : usey merey paas ley kar aa. main ley kar aaya to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : tera Rab kon hai? us ney kaha : Allah. aap ney farmaya : main kon hun? us ney kaha : aap Allah Taala key Rasool hain. aap ney farmaya : isey azad kar dey. ye momin hai."
3684,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Saad ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : meri walida faut ho gaee hai aur wo koi wasiyat nahin kar saki, to kya main (apney taur par) uski taraf sey sadqa kar dun? aap ney farmaya : haan."
3685,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri walida faut ho gaee hai. agar main uski taraf sey sadqa kar dun to kya usey faeyda hoga? aap ney farmaya : haan. us aadmi ney kaha : merey paas eik baagh hai. main aap ko gawah banata hun ke mainey uski taraf sey sadqa (waqf) kar diya hai.
3686,Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : meri walida faut ho gaee hain. unkey zimmey eik nazar thi. agar main un ki taraf sey ghulam azad kar dun to kya un sey (nazar ki) adaegi ho jaeygi? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum apni walida ki taraf sey ghulam azad kar saktey ho.
3687,Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us nazar key barey mein sawal kiya jo un ki walida key zimmey thi. aur wo usey pura karney sey pehley faut ho gaee thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ye nazar uski taraf sey puri kar do.
3688,Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke unhoney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us nazar key barey mein puchha jo un ki walida key zimmey thi aur wo nazar puri karney sey pehley faut ho gaeen thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ye nazar apni walida ki taraf sey puri kar do.
3689,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us nazar key barey mein puchha jo un ki walida key zimmey thi aur wo usey pura karney sey pehley faut ho gaee thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum uski taraf sey ada kar do."
3690,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us nazar key barey mein puchha jo un ki walida key zimmey thi lekin wo usey pura karney sey pehley faut ho gaee thi. aap ney farmaya : uski taraf sey tum usey pura kar do.
3691,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke meri walida mohtarma faut ho gaeen, jabkey unkey zimmey eik nazar thi. mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney mujhey wo nazar un ki taraf sey ada karney ka hukm diya."
3692,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us nazar key barey mein puchha jo un ki walida mohtarma key zimmey thi lekin wo uski adaegi sey pehley hi faut ho gaee thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum uski taraf sey ada kar do.
3693,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur arz kiya : meri walida mohtarma faut ho gaee hain. unkey zimmey eik nazar thi jisey wo pura na kar saken. aap ney farmaya : uski taraf sey tum puri kar do."
3694,Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri walida mohtarma faut ho gaee hain. kya main un ki taraf sey sadqa kar sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : haan. mainey arz kiya : kon sa sadqa ziyada fazilat rakhta hai? aap ney farmaya : pani pilaanaa.
3695,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : pani pilaanaa."
3696,Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke un ki walida faut ho gaeen to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : meri walida faut ho gaee hain to kya main un ki taraf sey sadqa kar dun? aap ney farmaya : haan. unhoney kaha : afzal sadqa kon sa hai? aap ney farmaya : pani pilaanaa. usi bina par Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney Madina mein sabeel qaaim kar di thi (taake musafir waghera kisi tangi key baghair har waqt pani pi saken).
3697,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : aey Abu-Zar ! main tujhey kamzor samajhta hun aur main terey liye wohi kuchh pasand karta hun jo apney liye pasand karta hun. to do aadmiyon ka bhi Ameer na ban'na aur na kisi yatim key maal ka sarparast banna.
3698,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey aur wo apney dada sey bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kaha : main faqir hun. merey paas kuchh nahin, haan merey paas eik yatim hai (jis key maal ka main sarparast hun). aap ney farmaya : to apney yatim key maal sey kha sakta hai lekin na to fuzul kharchi aur israaf ho, na (us ka maal) zaya karney wala aur na (us yatim key maal sey) koi jama punji bananey wala ho."
3699,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab ye aayat utri : (وَلاَ تَقْرَبُوْا مَالَ الْیَتِیْمِ اِلاَّ بِالَّتِیْ ھِیَ اَحْسَنُ),''aur tum yatim key maal key qarib na jaao magar intehai achchhey andaz sey.'' aur (اِنَّ الَّذِیْنَ یَاْکُلُوْنَ اَمْوَالَ الْیَتٰمٰی ظُلْماً),  ''jo log zulm key sath nahaq yatimon ka maal khatey hain … الخ.'' to logon ney yatimon key maal aur khaney peeney sey alehdgi ikhtiyar kar li. us sey musalmanon key liye mashaqqat paida hui, chunanche unhoney uski shikayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ki. phir Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (وَیَسْئَلُوْنَکَ عَنِ الْیَتٰمٰی قُلْ اِصْلاحٌ لَّھُمْ خَیْر … لَاَعْنَتَکُمْ),""log aap sey yatim bachchon (key sath rehney) key barey mein sawal kartey hain. keh dijiye : un ki islah karna bahut behtar hai … (aur agar Allah chahta to) tumhen takleef mein dal deta.''"
3700,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey Allah Taala key is farman : (اِنَّ الَّذِیْنَ یَاْکُلُوْنَ … ),  ''yaqinan jo log yatimon ka maal nahaq khatey hain … الخ.'' key barey mein marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : yatim jin logon key zere-saya parwarish pa rahey they (ye aayat sun kar) unhoney yatim ka khana peena alag kar diya yahan tak ke bartan bhi. lekin us sey musalmanon key liye mashaqqat paida hui, phir Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaar di : (وَاِنْ تُخَالِطُوْھُمْ فَاِخْوَانُکُمْ),""agar tum yatimon key sath mil-jul kar raho to koi harj nahin. wo tumharey (deeni) bhai hain."" goya Allah Taala ney unkey sath mil kar rehna jayez qarar dey diya."
3701,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : saat mohlik (nuksaandeh) kamon sey bacho. puchha gaya, aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kon sey hain? aap ney farmaya : Allah key sath shareek thehraana, jadu karna, jis jaan ko Allah Taala ney mohtaram banaya hai usey qatl kar dalna siwaye iskey ke haq key sath ho, sood khana, yatim ka maal khana, jang key din bhag jana aur paak daman bholi bhaali momin aurton par tohmat lagana."
